//     //  The controller contract acts as a proxy for all vaults. When a new vault base strategy is created, it is added to the controller contract and then all vault
//     //  functions become available through the controller. The user will use the controller to select a base strategy, customize the trading parameters (if applicable),
//     //  deposit into a vault, and withdraw from a vault. The owner will be able to change the initial cost to mint a strategy and vault minimum deposit amounts from
//     //  the controller. The owner will also view and fill open orders through the controller.
//     //
//     //   ____________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________
//     //  |                                                                                                                                                            |
//     //  |                                                                 CONTROLLER                                                                                 |
//     //  |____________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________|
//     //                           |                                                     
//     //                           |
//     //                           |
//     //                           |
//     //                           V
//     //   ____________________________________________________
//     //  |                                                    |          A vault is the contract that holds the base strategy.
//     //  |                                                    |          Some vaults will have customizable attributes, others
//     //  |                       VAULT                        |          will an 'as-is' strategy. Vaults hold the assets that
//     //  |                                                    |          the user chooses for their strategy and performs all  
//     //  |                                                    |          of the trading. A user can always remove their assets
//     //  |____________________________________________________|          from a vault at any point in time.
//     //      |             |               |              |              
//     //      |             |               |              |              
//     //      |             |               |              |              
//     //      V             V               V              V   
//     //   _____________________         ______________________
//     //  |                     |       |                      |          Once the user determines their strategy and pays to enter
//     //  |                     |       |                      |          the vault, a token is minted to represent their unique
//     //  |        TOKEN        |       |        TOKEN         |          trading details. Trading details cannot be altered once
//     //  |                     |       |                      |          the token is minted.
//     //  |_____________________|       |______________________|
//     //      |             |               |              |              
//     //      |             |               |              |              
//     //      |             |               |              |              
//     //      V             V               V              V   
//     //   _______       _______         _______        _______
//     //  |       |     |       |       |       |      |       |          Trades consist of the buy order(s), and resulting sell orders.
//     //  | Trade |     | Trade |       | Trade |      | Trade |          This is used purely for informational purposes.
//     //  |_______|     |_______|       |_______|      |_______|
//     //   |     |       |     |         |     |        |     |      
//     //   |     |       |     |         |     |        |     |      
//     //   V     V       V     V         V     V        V     V      
//     //  ___   ___     ___   ___       ___   ___      ___   ___
//     // |   | |   |   |   | |   |     |   | |   |    |   | |   |         Orders are either Buy or Sell. They hold the specific 
//     // | O | | O |   | O | | O |     | O | | O |    | O | | O |         order details of path, buy/sell signals, from amount,
//     // | R | | R |   | R | | R |     | R | | R |    | R | | R |         limit amount, and any other trading information.
//     // | D | | D |   | D | | D |     | D | | D |    | D | | D |
//     // | E | | E |   | E | | E |     | E | | E |    | E | | E |
//     // | R | | R |   | R | | R |     | R | | R |    | R | | R |
//     // |___| |___|   |___| |___|     |___| |___|    |___| |___|





